---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="About • Historical Translation Project™">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pt-10 pb-16">
    <div class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-gold">ABOUT</div>
    <h1 class="mt-2 font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-navy">A research-first mission</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-muted text-lg max-w-3xl">
      We continue researching ancient remedies throughout the globe and history—bringing them together with modern, reputable knowledge in a compliance-first way.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="rounded-xl2 bg-card shadow-soft border border-line p-6 lg:col-span-2">
        <p class="text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Historical Translation Project™ studies primary medical texts across cultures and eras, translating durable preventive principles into clear modern language.
          We do not offer medical advice and we do not make disease treatment claims. Instead, we publish educational dossiers and develop botanical formulations using structure/function language.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Project 01 focuses on Rambam’s preventive framework—digestion, rhythm, moderation, and preservation of vitality—serving as the methodological template for future projects.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl2 bg-parchment border border-line p-6">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-navy">Core principles</div>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-muted">
          <li>Contextual translation</li>
          <li>Evidence-forward sourcing</li>
          <li>Compliance-first language</li>
          <li>Safety + interactions disclosed</li>
          <li>Premium presentation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
